casebody.data:
Stephen V. KOLBE, et al., petitioners,
v.
Lawrence J. HOGAN, Jr., Governor of Maryland, et al. No. 17-127. Supreme Court of the United States Nov. 27, 2017.

Motion of Edwin Vieira, Jr., et al. for leave to file a brief as amici curiae granted. Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Fourth Circuit denied.
